{"tid":1518713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學生罷課其實冇撚用","createTime":"2019-08-30T10:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T13:43:22.000Z","uid":307316,"like":79,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"59959b8782cf08b51ff4018dcc3e31e7455c86af","tid":1518713,"uid":307316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"梗係冇撚用啦屌 個個淨係坐喺禮堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2/9罷課學校淨係比室內鳩坐自修 咁叫罷課咩屌？根本同上堂冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果學校淨係比鳩坐 咁不如出去愛丁堡個集會 因為依家好多學校寧願叫學生 交家長相請假去罷課 都唔想校內自己搞呀<br />\n自己諗下啦 鳩坐有撚用 仲要鳩坐唔報人數比罷課統計 罷黎有撚用冇人會知㗎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tTHBDcr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtTHBDcr.jpg&h=cbcf3817&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HfzpSs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HfzpSs.jpg&h=bc23dbc0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RwtEAY8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwtEAY8.jpg&h=2dae1d69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BBVPdLP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBBVPdLP.jpg&h=36cc2673&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"964e35881ea915a528a5417b85c9899659e2332c","tid":1518713,"uid":123991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUQvG7y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUQvG7y.gif&h=0b84475f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUikUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=e605e559\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%