62755a575c90033e53ac262f539f9","tid":1518713,"uid":145884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:42:44.000Z","msg":"巴打我都有咁嘅諗法 歡迎想將罷課升級嘅中學生入嚟睇下呢個post <br />\n[重開］全部中學生同我入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1516206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1516206</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n利申 非騎劫 各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7d3763b4e4045e6fb2aedf93390d23d09060c2","tid":1518713,"uid":278971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門！"},{"pid":"3d5a46f799492f01feba440101ec5509f986d197","tid":1518713,"uid":45477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"應該要搵個地方集合晒唔同學校學生靜坐罷課"},{"pid":"214b03dc575d7a569de755abe801a271d5caa535","tid":1518713,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"守護學生妹行動 <br />\n<br />\n一開學啲狗仔會似住自己有特權，四圍去搞啲女同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本唔係罷課唔罷課嘅問題，而係呢個時候開學真係好危險<br />\n<br />\n如其他同學在學校被警務人員子女欺凌，大家一定要出聲<br />\n<br />\n我已經預計到，佢地會對其他男同學陏手陏腳，對女同學就摸手摸腳<br />\n<br />\n「你係唔係唔畀我打？你係唔係唔畀我摸？我同學校講你歧視我」<br />\n<br />\n大家千祈唔好啞忍，咁嘅欺凌行為只會越嚟越嚴重"},{"pid":"d8c1625f2156f9a3548a8024287dca53b7e5cc77","tid":1518713,"uid":107561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:01:39.000Z","msg":"推呀推上熱門"},{"pid":"cdb4c784372163942508b3a484d3b9a892f2433c","tid":1518713,"uid":284804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:14:21.000Z","msg":"要爭氣啊 罷課真係唔洗驚班奶共教畜 想點搞就點搞 人多就冇事"},{"pid":"7b1c17ce7d3dbca4d2698e5225f19eeeecb22f38","tid":1518713,"uid":62167,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:16:35.000Z","msg":"其實中學生唔需要太介意操行<br />\n冇人會睇<br />\n只會睇DSE成績"},{"pid":"835296564178c8ef197d7dc12f3f6e5795e7e588","tid":1518713,"uid":179380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:22:49.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"bb8f6a3eb007d7bf9a906b8c31089bb1e3be8b0a","tid":1518713,"uid":134854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/De29XVe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDe29XVe.png&h=fb5f20fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月31 自由行 下午三點見<br />\n被禁也要出"},{"pid":"c1bf0edd1aadb4b6eb8ed81ef07dfa4941cba913","tid":1518713,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:24:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf98c1bcebbafc763b9fe6b597435f3da9bade1c","tid":1518713,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"罷課依啲唔講啦<br />\n想講既係罷唔到課既小朋友可以做咩<br />\n<br />\n除左唔同啲犬二代玩，保障自己之外<br />\n你仲可以做好多野<br />\n<br />\n1.尋找志同道合既朋友仔<br />\n學生始終係中意埋堆玩，容易受人影響，可以weekend約埋去行下街，買下玩具，咁就唔怕單機啦，個圈仲可以日漸擴大，感染下啲唔敢出既人<br />\n<br />\n2.善用壁布<br />\n文宣咁靚，梗係趁班主任未到就釘哂上去<br />\n美化下課室<br />\n<br />\n3.乜都傾一餐<br />\n之前乜事都冇就傾下 kpop 傾下八卦 傾下動漫<br />\n但依家日日新鮮<br />\n一翻到去梗係同同學傾餐飽啦<br />\n琴日班狗有幾柒 佢地有幾賤<br />\n上線前應該有咩戰術(講梗打機)<br />\n買咩 gear  去邊課金(講梗打機)<br />\n小息講放學講轉堂講<br />\n課室操埸教員室門囗都係好地方<br />\n傾下計都比老師捉？咁個老師等比人篤灰啦<br />\n<br />\n4.尋找山區小孩/助養者<br />\n如果你好有需要/屋企人有助養開<br />\n不妨向身邊人求救/ 伸出援手<br />\n<br />\n不過睇到嘅學生可能得好少， 希望你哋喺學校都可以有個好開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6c05c76ec2645cafcd29ca821cdbd52197a5e3","tid":1518713,"uid":202463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:26:47.000Z","msg":"VC人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"