://na.cx/i/RwtEAY8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwtEAY8.jpg&h=2dae1d69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BBVPdLP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBBVPdLP.jpg&h=36cc2673&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"返學啦<br />\n同狗仔狗女攪好關係<br />\n第時過關唔洗check手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:44:31.000Z","msg":"冇咩都唔返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46c9bc02c26d94d2969af39f448342962b7a334","tid":1518713,"uid":282058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:46:10.000Z","msg":"我愛00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabf9aa245f49c2011c4ab6b5b040d37a27432b3","tid":1518713,"uid":207232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"我以前間中學不嬲請兩日假要醫生紙 <br />\n一日淨係要家長信<br />\n有次試過連請兩日假 <br />\n唔撚見咗張醫生紙 學校記曠課<br />\n咪又係升到班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知你地怕乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：一年請十幾日假"},{"pid":"401efc89e6782e25de744ad6ce2abb0836af0232","tid":1518713,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:57:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1518918/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1518918/page/1</a><br />\n為了防止狗賊唔比搵律師，請各位義士發夢之前搵一個信得過既家人或者朋友交低一個時間，例如我今日去夢遊, 若果我在夜晚2200之前無報平安, 就等於出左事, 要搵律師。地點可能有少少麻煩, 要走幾轉先知, 但係都好過比人拉48個鐘。當然佢要知道你既身份證號碼同中英文全名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/xz7tbmcbmkj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%